  <brief_title>Lamivudine Plus Adefovir Versus Telbivudine Plus Adefovir in Lamivudine Resistant Chronic Hepatitis B</brief_title>
  <official_title>Antiviral Efficacy of Continuing Lamivudine Plus Adefovir or Switching to Telbivudine Plus Adefovir in HBeAg-positive Lamivudine-refractory Chronic Hepatitis B Patients Who Have Suboptimal Response to Lamivudine Plus Adefovir for at Least 12 Months</official_title>
